query:
SELECT inspectionId, stationKey, id, component, location, tActual
FROM tmlReadings
WHERE stationKey IS NOT NULL AND stationKey != ''
AND (inspectionId, stationKey) IN (
  SELECT inspectionId, stationKey
  FROM tmlReadings
  WHERE stationKey IS NOT NULL AND stationKey != ''
  GROUP BY inspectionId, stationKey
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
  LIMIT 1
)
ORDER BY inspectionId, stationKey
LIMIT 10;
